== 反響 ==
約翰·麥克連的動作硬漢角色形象與布魯斯·威利的演出已深獲影評人和觀眾的歡迎。《[[帝國雜誌|帝國雜誌]]》將約翰·麥克連列在「時時刻刻百大電影人物」中的第十二名<ref name="empire">{{cite web|url=http://www.empireonline.com/100-greatest-movie-characters/default.asp?c=12|title=The 100 Greatest Movie Characters|work=Empire Online|accessdate=2016-11-25|archive-date=2013-04-20|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6G1CiZnFe?url=http://www.empireonline.com/100-greatest-movie-characters/default.asp?c=12|dead-url=no}}</ref>。據[[MTV|MTV]]調查，演員和粉絲所評選的「史上最偉大的電影無賴」中，麥克連位居第三，僅次於{{tsl|en|Ellen Ripley|艾倫·雷普利}}與[[骯髒哈利|骯髒哈利]]<ref>{{cite web |last=Carroll |first=Larry |url=http://www.mtv.com/news/articles/1604506/20090206/story.jhtml |title=Our Greatest Movie Badass Of All Time Is ... |publisher=MTV |date=2009-02-06 |accessdate=2011-11-18 |archive-date=2013-04-20 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6G1CjTbQl?url=http://www.mtv.com/news/articles/1604506/our-greatest-movie-badass-all-time.jhtml |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

